<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>红光灸</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<style>
  body {
    background: url('/images/redlight.jpeg') no-repeat center center fixed;
    background-size: cover;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #333;
  }

  .overlay {
    background-color: rgba(255, 240, 240, 0.9); /* light warm tint */
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    background-color: #ffffffcc;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 180, 180, 0.2);
  }

  .big-paragraph {
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    font-size: 1.0rem;
  }

  .formatted-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    font-family: inherit; /* Optional: keep normal font */
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
  }

  .content-text {
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    font-size: 1.2em; /* Optional: increase font size */
    line-height: 1.6;  /* Optional: more readable spacing */
  }

  }

</style>


</head>

<body class="p-4">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>🔥 红光灸 🔥</h1>
    <div class="content-text">
       <p>       红光灸，也叫近红外光疗。是利用波长在600至1100纳米之间的红光与近红外光，通过一定功率照射身体局部，达到温通经络、活血化瘀、祛寒止痛的目的。这种特定波长的光能把热力渗透到皮下，刺激组织，类似于我们传统针刺加艾灸中的温热作用，但它无烟、无火、更便于操作。</p>
       <p>       在中医的理解中，这类温热刺激，也属于“火热之气”，能够补阳祛寒，通行气血，尤其适用于寒凝血瘀、阳虚不通等证型。它解决了艾灸烟大、味重、操作不便的问题，还可以与中药外敷膏剂结合使用，让理疗效果再上一个台阶。
       </p>
     </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="accordion" id="accordionCh">
      <% items.forEach((item, index) => { %>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingCh<%= index %>">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseCh<%= index %>">
              <%= item.c_title %>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseCh<%= index %>" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionCh">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <pre class="big-paragraph"><%- item.c_description %></pre>
              <% if (item.image_url) { %>
                 <img src="<%= item.image_url %>" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" style="height: auto;" alt="Image">
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
  </div>

<div style="position: fixed; top: 10px; right: 10px; z-index: 1000;">
  <a href="/admin" style="font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9; text-decoration: none;">⚙️</a>
</div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

